data.description: Welcome home to your beautiful country home, surrounded by nature and privacy, with coveted basement and master on main, all within the highly desired Cherokee school district!!! Stunning living room upon entry with lots of natural light and gleaming hardwoods lead into the spacious kitchen with warm earth tones, TONS of cabinet space and eat in area. The master bedroom an adjoining bathroom suite with master closet provide ample space for comfortable living. Upstairs provides an additional two bedrooms with a shared bathroom, and the unfinished basement offers lots of space for future expansion if desired. Outdoor features like gorgeous wrap around porch with patio seating on the level below, a bonus balcony/porch off the kitchen, lots of level yard space and level driveway, attached two car garage, storage shed, and fiberoptics available!! You'll absolutely appreciate all that this peaceful home retreat has to offer. This charming property won't last long!! Schedule your showings today!!
